<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <!-- here is the head -->
  <%- include ../partial/head.ejs %>
  <body>
    <!-- here is the header -->
    <%- include ../partial/header.ejs %>
    <!-- body of the page -->
    <div class="bg-container container about">
      <div id="aboutBanner" class="carousel carousel-dark slide carousel-fade" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#aboutBanner" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true"
            aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active" data-bs-interval="2000">
            <img class="img-fluid d-block rounded-4 w-100" src="/images/about.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5 class="text-start fw-bold fs-1 text-dark">Business blends <br />Tech and Design</h5>
              <p class="text-start fw-light fs-5 text-black-50">From marketer to designer, developer to AI</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4">
            <div class="p-5">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                  <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block rounded-circle" src="/images/hugo.jpeg" alt="Resume">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-8">
            <div class="p-1">
              <h2 class="display-5 text-start fw-bold fs-2 text-dark">About Hugo</h2>
              <p class="text-start fw-light fs-5 text-black-50">
                My name is Hugo Mak (Chung Ping MAK) and I am a highly motivated individual with a unique blend of
                business acumen and design expertise. My background in business and design, along with my passion for
                detail and aesthetics, has allowed me to bring a human-centered approach to the development of various
                web and mobile applications. Through years of self-taught programming, I have become a skilled
                programmer and have had the opportunity of leading a programming team to work with well-known
                companies, educational institutions, and professional associations in Hong Kong. I am the founder of
                my own digital agency and have extensive experience in web and mobile application development. As a
                serial entrepreneur, programmer, and businessman, I am always looking for new challenges and
                opportunities to grow. Currently, I am furthering my education in AI at Centennial College, eager to
                stay ahead of the curve and bring cutting-edge solutions to my clients.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
            <div class="p-5">
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                  <h2 class="display-5 text-start fw-bold fs-2 text-dark">Resume</h2>
                  <p class="text-start fw-light fs-5 text-black-50">
                    I am always seeking new challenges and opportunities for growth. Please refer to my CV for further
                    details.
                    <br>
                    <a class="mt-3 btn btn-dark" target="_blank" href="/doc/hugo-mak-cv.pdf">Resume</a>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
            <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" src="/images/vacant.png" alt="Resume">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- here is the footer -->
    <%- include ../partial/footer.ejs %>
    <!-- here are the js script -->
    <%- include ../partial/script.ejs %>
  </body>
</html>